						<summary>

						<p>Broken slab lying near the Chāvaḍi.</p>						

						<p>The date portion of the record is not clear. It mentions only the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Yuva, Mārgaśira.</hi> However, on the basis of palaeography, it may be assigned to the 13th century.</p>						

						<p>Fragment. It seems to record the sale of land to Akajiya. It also mentions Tippajiya and Sōmajiya.</p>						

						</summary>
